Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,

<% case @rule.operator.to_sym %>
<% when :eq %>
  This email is to notify you that Cap City's <%= @item_name %> stock is currently at <%= @rule.threshold %>.
<% when :lt %>
  This email is to notify you that Cap City's <%= @item_name %> stock has fallen below <%= @rule.threshold %>.
<% when :lt_eq %>
  This email is to notify you that Cap City's <%= @item_name %> stock has dropped to <%= @rule.threshold %>.
<% when :gt %>
  This email is to notify you that Cap City's <%= @item_name %> stock has grown past <%= @rule.threshold %>.
<% when :gt %>
  This email is to notify you that Cap City's <%= @item_name %> stock has reached <%= @rule.threshold %>.
<% end %>

You can view the full Cap City inventory at <%= inventory_categories_url %>.
